# 🌤 Weather App (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)

A fully responsive Weather Application using the [OpenWeatherMap API](https://openweathermap.org/) built with **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**.

---

## 📖 Overview

This Weather App allows users to search for any city and get **real-time weather information**. It also maintains a search history using browser local storage and provides extra details such as humidity, wind speed, and sunrise/sunset times.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 **Search any city** and get live weather data.
- 🌡 **Current temperature, weather description, and icons**.
- 🌍 Displays **city and country name**.
- 💨 **Additional details**:
  - Feels like temperature
  - Humidity
  - Pressure
  - Wind speed
  - Sunrise and sunset times
- 🕘 **Date and time** auto-updated.
- 📜 **Search history** (last 10 searches) stored in local storage.
- 🧹 Option to **clear history**.
- 💻 Fully **responsive and clean design**.

