## 🛠 Technologies Used

- **HTML5** – App structure
- **CSS3** – Modern styling (gradients, shadows, responsive design)
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – Fetch API, DOM manipulation, and local storage
- **OpenWeatherMap API** – Weather data provider

